360
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:54,359
A fost minţit.

361
00:32:54,519 --> 00:32:57,193
I-au spus că turnurile emit raze.

362
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,992
Iar el i-a crezut.

363
00:32:59,279 --> 00:33:00,599
